{"tid":489314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳張陽曾給郭文貴200枝槍 因政變流產被自殺","createTime":"2017-12-04T14:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T14:55:24.000Z","uid":53705,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"3b9bbef0ce112a86546830fe48195db72e0c45c7","tid":489314,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:26:45.000Z","msg":"中共中央軍委政治工作部前主任張陽，日前驚傳於本月23日在家中自縊身亡。美國中文媒體博聞社獨家報導，<span style=\"color: red;\">張陽很可能涉及流產武裝政變，包括富商郭文貴在美不斷爆料，也是政變計畫的一環，張陽可能曾給郭200枝槍及2000萬人民幣（約9000萬台幣）。而張陽之死可能是「被自殺」以滅口。 </span><br />\n<br />\n博聞社指出，張陽一名前警衛人員23日進入張的家中，稱要給他治療，警衛離開後，張即被發現上吊死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n博聞社稱，張陽的秘書遭到秘審時供稱曾給郭200枝槍，這批槍從中國銷往非洲某國，再入境秘送到北京燕郊某處，不過，郭文貴對此事至今沒有回應。 <br />\n<br />\n公開資料顯示，現年66歲的張陽在徐才厚主管的軍隊政工系統任職多年，歷任中共42集團軍政治部主任、政委、廣州軍區政治部主任，2007年任中共原廣州軍區政治委員，中共十八大前夕擔任中共原總政治部主任，軍改後任中共軍委政工部主任。"},{"pid":"4f13f74e9516a94d64d4f583c2585c01c24197d3","tid":489314,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"200枝槍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a06f5d2d4ca1476553d2162f3e32c23b510e77","tid":489314,"uid":76115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:47:41.000Z","msg":"雖采200枝少左啲不過威力應該都勁過世界排華史.jpg"},{"pid":"f1736868e65a73780f57d0826466ee7f812c2e65","tid":489314,"uid":22858,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T14:48:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖采200枝少左啲不過威力應該都勁過世界排華史.jpg</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/081643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F081643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3be43dfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2bb2d6211ca8216de1c94fedb62ed55089b8b4e3","tid":489314,"uid":40216,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:32:49.000Z","msg":"大局已定仲搞乜政變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70a9e1dbfbd97b2235ab9b2efc4a3669d459e11","tid":489314,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:34:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大局已定仲搞乜政變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雜種想推翻自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e1d1875b0da2a90185737cad5664fb07bda1e7","tid":489314,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"200枝槍搞政變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4eda01b89cb8e621c1961aaa75c1dbcb9d902c","tid":489314,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"幾時強姦隻豬"},{"pid":"73aed8ba697c39acf61cee2fab0967d51756092d","tid":489314,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>200枝槍搞政變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n在精 在快 不在多<br />\n200枝槍唔多 但都唔係小......<br />\n<br />\n殺左雜種<br />\n其餘果堆自然鳥獸散"},{"pid":"1118957a73cb754414f0ae4eb5fe8913d61a8503","tid":489314,"uid":118360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:34:49.000Z","msg":"郭文貴係咪黐撚左線<br />\n買中國製o既槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c1a3afe24f1c4dd51235ef78c561a4d45e56cb","tid":489314,"uid":91432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T18:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde00bb77d18d8610b224ca9de16c1429d935327","tid":489314,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-