l/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n在精 在快 不在多<br />\n200枝槍唔多 但都唔係小......<br />\n<br />\n殺左雜種<br />\n其餘果堆自然鳥獸散</blockquote><br />\n連登軍事專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f764cf15b78287dce03f376e87c7be11073ac5","tid":489314,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T00:35:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>200枝槍搞政變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n在精 在快 不在多<br />\n200枝槍唔多 但都唔係小......<br />\n殺左雜種<br />\n其餘果堆自然鳥獸散</blockquote><br />\n連登軍事專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本能寺之變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359087babbc66a7b1e377caab8b8a6f138c3321a","tid":489314,"uid":37735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:13:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>200枝槍搞政變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n在精 在快 不在多<br />\n200枝槍唔多 但都唔係小......<br />\n<br />\n殺左雜種<br />\n其餘果堆自然鳥獸散</blockquote><br />\n連登軍事專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係自吹軍事專家<br />\n只係講歴史事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人類劣根性  大多數人都會見風轉陀<br />\n只係為搵著數  一見勢不對 就會烏獸散<br />\n咩恩情 道義 1000個入面999個都管他的<br />\n<br />\n玄武門又好<br />\n上面講本能寺<br />\n<br />\n本能寺殺左信長<br />\n信長一死 織田家極速玩完 是一堆人話要報仇  但真心的有邊個 (咩猴子 最後迫死人個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n呢個上將以前係徐才厚的人  <br />\n佢同房曉輝(個名類似是咁)有關<br />\n甚至可能同江澤民有關係<br />\n<br />\n只要殺左習近平 無左權力核心者<br />\n郭文貴 口中的老幹部 慶親王 宋祖英老公<br />\n<br />\n唔洗任何野  都一堆李鴻忠之流跳糟<br />\n<br />\n西班牙長槍黨真正死因唔是佛朗哥死左<br />\n是佢個老友同繼承人  被 巴斯克挖地道 <br />\n炸死左 (左派，左膠唔會講 只會講不流血)"},{"pid":"53cedd0c7c030e660089477aab7266530061ee06","tid":489314,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>200枝槍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n200聽眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (某網絡大台)"},{"pid":"d05bccd4172add979884d789c3cef404e9ed8a7c","tid":489314,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:17:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>200枝槍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n200聽眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (某網絡大台)"},{"pid":"288f9ca558d8afcf67318ce63b0de6d1e59020ef","tid":489314,"uid":21880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:26:19.000Z","msg":"200枝槍都算喇，2000萬元就想學人搞政變，香港求其一個豪宅都唔只啦。<br />\n<br />\n咁都搞得掂，唔怪得咁怕搞港獨啦，香港咁多有錢人。"}]}